      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VISTA YTTRIUM (4) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Scored by 7 lengths last time (19.43) in a Grade 5 over 340m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. COWBOY CARTER (3) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 2.5 lengths second over 340m at this track, clocking 19.74. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from six starts. Must be included in calculations. LAURIE'S FERRARI (2) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including four wins. Below best last time at The Gardens (23.49) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 7 length fourth. Suited here and expected to run well. NOAH BONKERS (7) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
